    "causal_summary": "The code graph (tree-sitter→SQLite typed edges) mutates edges destructively on incremental reindex, lacks idempotent edge IDs and a hard readiness watermark, ranks impact with flat edge walks, and skips doc-lane symbols. Aionforge encodes non-destructive bi-temporal lifecycle, content-addressed IDs, quarantine-not-wedge recovery, and generation-checked readiness.",
